#: 21337012-0-5122
msgctxt "21337012-0-5122"
msgid "The sea before the serpent-prow did break."
"\nThe wind was trapped inside the black-cloth sails."
"\nThe pounding drum did mask the rower's wails,"
"\nAnd demons of the sea swam in the wake."
"\n"
"\nA dark rain fell as though a widow's veil,"
"\nAlong with lightning-flash and thunder-peal,"
"\nViscarne the butcher grasped his vessel's wheel"
"\nThe villain of a thousand fractured tales."
"\n"
"\nHe did not spare his blade from those who kneel,"
"\nOr from the young, the weak, the sick, the old."
"\nThe cruelty in his heart was often told,"
"\nAnd those that faced his blade would never heal."
"\n"
"\nThe target of the grim fleet was Sunhold. "
"\nAn Altmer prize long sought by Orgnum-king—"
"\nThe golden port once graced with gryphon wing,"
"\nA victory that would not go untold."
"\n"
"\nViscarne sailed in, so our ancestors sing."
"\nBut found a harbor empty now, and still."
"\nNo ships to burn, no innocents to kill."
"\nNo one to feel the serpent's bitter sting."
"\n"
"\nThen from the palace sitting on the hill,"
"\nAn army dressed in gold came riding forth."
"\nA crushing wave of Altmer from the north,"
"\nTo bring the sun's warmth to the Maormer chill."
"\n"
"\nThey killed Viscarne's second, third, and fourth,"
"\nThe butcher's ships were burning in the bay."
"\nThe Maormer knew that he had lost the day,"
"\nHis forces fallen having shown their lack of worth."
msgstr "海はサーペントの舳先の前に割れ\\r"
"\n風は黒い布の帆船に捕らえられた\\r"
"\n打ち鳴らされる鼓は漕ぎ手の苦悶を隠し\\r"
"\n海の悪魔が後を追って泳いだ\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n暗い雨が寡婦のベールのように降り注ぎ\\r"
"\n稲光と雷鳴を従え\\r"
"\n虐殺者ヴィスカルネは船の舵輪を掴んだ。\\r"
"\n砕け散った千の物語の悪党。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n彼は膝をついた者も容赦なく刃にかけた\\r"
"\n若き者、弱き者、病人、老人をも\\r"
"\nその心の残忍さはしばし語られ\\r"
"\nその刃にまみえた者は、決して癒えることなし\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n残忍な艦隊の標的はサンホールド\\r"
"\nオルグヌム王が求め続けたアルトマーの獲物\\r"
"\nかつてグリフォンの翼を授けられた黄金の港\\r"
"\n語られずにはおかれぬ勝利\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nヴィスカルネは船を乗り入れた、と我らが先人は歌う\\r"
"\nだが港はもはや空っぽ、動くものとてなし\\r"
"\n焼く船もなし、殺すべき無実の者もなし\\r"
"\nサーペントの苦い一突きを味わう者はなし\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nすると丘にそびえる宮殿より\\r"
"\n黄金をまとった一軍が突撃した\\r"
"\n北からのアルトマーの圧倒的な波\\r"
"\nマオマーの冷気に太陽のぬくもりをもたらすため\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n彼らはヴィスカルネの副官を次々殺し\\r"
"\n虐殺者の艦隊は港にて燃え上がった\\r"
"\nマオマーは彼の敗北を知り\\r"
"\n彼の勢力は斃れ、その無力を示した"

