msgid "Though they may be hidden well,"
"\nI see where these relics dwell."
"\nIn order to stop this shadowy theft,"
"\nOne must go to Summerset."
"\n"
"\nThe Lantern of Lies, with malicious glow,"
"\nCan be found by the rocks of Welenkin Cove."
"\nWithin the crevice of coral stone,"
"\nWhere coral crabs have made their home."
