"\nSearch the Alinor Dock's rightmost pier,"
"\nFor the Silver-Tongued Quill sits near."
"\n"
"\nIn Rellenthil, home of players great,"
"\nThe Unraveling Staff lies in wait."
"\nBeneath a bridge, by gentle creek,"
"\nYou'll find the relic that you seek."
"\n"
"\nNear the Russafeld wayshrine,"
"\nSits a skull without a spine."
"\nThe Skull of Minor Cursing hides,"
"\nOn cliff's edge, near sinkhole wide."
"\n"
