"\n"
"\nNear the Illumination Academy,"
"\nHides another relic of tragedy."
"\nYou'll find the Never-Ending Scroll,"
"\nBeside the bridge that has no toll."
"\n"
"\nWithin the ruins of Corgrad Wastes,"
"\nThe Inescapable Helm awaits."
"\nLook beneath a twisted tree,"
