"\n"
"\nOverlooking the coral queen,"
"\nIn a small forest, so serene,"
"\nThe Sticky-Fingered Lute shall be,"
"\nHidden near a royal hatchery."
"\n"
"\nOn Northern beach, by waterfall,"
"\nPlaced against a stony wall,"
"\nBeyond where angry gryphons pace,"
"\nHides the Fan of False-Face."
"\n"
"\nBetween a ruined Direnni home,"
