msgid "Dear Norasea,"
"\n"
"\nMy heart breaks at this dreadful news. You must come to Lillandril at once! The Sapiarchs have ample resources. I promise you, we will cure this affliction, no matter the cost."
"\n"
"\nI've met someone. His name is Emile, and he possesses a rare gift when it comes to the arts of healing and restoration. Between the three of us, we will find a way to restore your good health. I swear it."
